author: Flo
content:
Thanks, Andreas, for explaining what you did with the Sophisticated Lady image. Sounds complicated, but once you've done it a few times, I guess it would be easier and flow more quickly, too.

This image for Tuesday may look like you're beginning to feel, lol. Perhaps this is why you chose it? Perhaps you'd benefit by hiring this clearing out service? LOL. Clear disorder out of your life's scheduling?
